{"tid":1632901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解連登冇被ddos，因為好多分化post，大家要小心睇post","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:54:27.000Z","uid":130601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4568aeb6d06b1f5f5364155457abe36fe7b048","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:00:43.000Z","msg":"我先唔評論個九龍遊行鬼唔鬼<br />\n但陸續見到好多負面情緒post出黎，想打心理戰<br />\n大家情緒可能會受不少影響<br />\n一係咁，唔識得分辨嘅話可以放鬆少少<br />\n休息一下再回來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n以下2個係例子，分析得好好<br />\n大家加油<br />\n<br />\n終於知道政府宜加打緊咩牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n上緊連登既你 一個二個放低電話 暫時遠離連登！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631560</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫我推唔該，大家小心閱讀</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"c930e136c00560a58bd010126182ea2f91b9698a","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83d3dfc21c63c229ea6fdb5011bb6b1b16d2c1b3","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:01:42.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"340e8519698bb862096cdee67b02a2ead681b7d0","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"小心有分化"},{"pid":"a5375300ad02874cab84f00085049a36c56a53d0","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:02:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94e8bbf2506abf06fe0ad9257adb987846b71c38","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:02:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"107d7936d089814dd09f794ac057983b6e5f21e3","tid":1632901,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:02:44.000Z","msg":"人民日報：騷亂大致平息，禁蒙面法成功殺菌消毒<br />\n<br />\n內地《人民日報》在微博，發表題為「禁止蒙面，為香港殺菌消毒」的評論文章。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，特區政府果斷訂立《禁止蒙面規例》，可謂必要、及時；又說從單區騷亂到「遍地開花」、從街頭打砸到室內縱火、從摧毀公共設施到破壞普通商戶、從圍攻警員到群毆市民，暴徒膽子越來越大，暴行危害越來越重，反問香港已滋生恐怖主義、淪為罪惡氾濫之地，再不採取更有力度的措施止暴制亂，何以守護這個城市。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，暴徒所以走上「狂暴之路」，變成極惡之人，多與蒙面有關，又認為訂立規例，不意味香港已進入緊急狀態，不會損害市民合法、和平、自由表達意見的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人民日報終於有得岩返次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3090f845db41b87e9836d89f02cd9b9a63d4ce","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:02:54.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"a49f954f870947065a3e03b9d2cf9838691afaab","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:03:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aca63a9fa92b88a31dcb61ca929dc28c99d018c4","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"俾多啲人見到"},{"pid":"35dece5bd958380cc5d4a751bd2870427b202b62","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"加油啊"},{"pid":"a0481325cdb50e4c9d36b7dd58a835cc3cd73ed1","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"比多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"47f4d55899d77b3f3a0ea464e5955504ef65bbe8","tid":1632901,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:05:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"042e733a20fe274eddbacc1ad4291356463e38ee","tid":1632901,"uid":97900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"be4f423d5379c2183727b504f4486e781b43a882","tid":1632901,"uid":42855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"push"}]}